{"tid":1519521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"認真 聽日唔該偽勇武企返後面做個和理非","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T02:59:32.000Z","uid":22131,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74d98921d4c01f0a16217375faa1b594b06dae21","tid":1519521,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"雖然話聽日路線係要人多加和理非<br />\n但有gear一定上gear先 以防萬一<br />\n基本上再be water都總有一兩條線要同班黑狗對陣<br />\n<br />\n如果冇心理準備對抗 被捕 打狗既<br />\n立即企返後 <br />\n如果冇心理準備滅煙 投擲 救人既<br />\n再企返後<br />\n<br />\n同前排兩線人最少保持一定距離15-20米(?)<br />\n有起事上黎 唔好塞住曬<br />\n再因應情況 睇前線意見再決定推 守 還是退<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喂 我上曬full gear防爆眼罩,頭盔,史詩豬嘴</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我縮係後面咪好柒 好樣衰？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n勇武講既唔單止係裝備 更講究決心<br />\n你上曬裝 一遇狗衝就走既話 咁你根本上就係和理非<br />\n你夾硬上前線 會令前線計錯人數 好易錯判 影響行動<br />\n更衰既會令手足流更多血 更多手足被班狗捉到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你想樣衰咁做後排？定好型咁令手足被捕？</span></span><br />\n所以冇決心既 寧願你企返後面 至少前線既會知道有狗衝埋黎時 佢隔離果個係可能會對抗 唔會只係即刻逃跑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位手足聽日平安 武運亨昌<br />\n不被捕 不流血 不割䉀 不捉鬼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe657286eb1e76b110a2b8b8c01a4a6898bfd8f7","tid":1519521,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3434dd6c112a945b6ba62afdfc286b29857cf6e","tid":1519521,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=78031108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=110344a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=e603a961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=b7d8fef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"6492db9f233e42ce04aa102aaa0b5bce074e97d1","tid":1519521,"uid":22131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你想樣衰咁做後排？定好型咁令手足被捕？</span></span>"},{"pid":"99092c3e9093a56da0371b8f7f72e495e08d5ef8","tid":1519521,"uid":264626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得721 之後個日又話刀手又性，屯天元連銀行都落閘，最後有無事吖？<br />\n<br />\n聽日和理非一定要出，唔係要你衝，你自認和理非既，你就要相信「理」，你去行街可以告你D乜！？<br />\n<br />\n聽日絕對係人數決定一切！<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"756122c89f1fe255d5d7416cb348384d6671d1ac","tid":1519521,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你想樣衰咁做後排？<br />\n定好型咁令手足被捕？</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd5098dd572200e119f8a2a1b39abd4f1654340f","tid":1519521,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再講聽日最後一戰！10月1號都未到最咩後一戰！對家就真係想係最後一戰，唔洗拖到10月1</span></span>"},{"pid":"cef36465efd8927bde1e97fbb836aedf744c8112","tid":1519521,"uid":46720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de20bea3a21cc3e543f17f4d2340d610e6d925","tid":1519521,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c888a1f082138d56b9df336c3a6d317499ceaf","tid":1519521,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你想樣衰咁做後排？<br />\n定好型咁令手足被捕？</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fd33ee040b53f9135114aef07c77c31833576d1","tid":1519521,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"大家唔係約定好 贏嘅時候 要除低口罩煲底相見咩<br />\n仲未到嗰個時候呀 仲未係最後呀<br />\n一齊堅持到贏唯止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">約定大家 光復到香港嗰一刻 煲底見</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[小心風向]最後一戰？？？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論